\hypertarget{structaurora_1_1_calibration_data}{}\doxysection{aurora\+::Calibration\+Data Struct Reference}
\label{structaurora_1_1_calibration_data}\index{aurora::CalibrationData@{aurora::CalibrationData}}


Calibration data container for Aurora This data is calibrated from the Qu-\/\+Bit default Aurora firmware. It is advised not to save over this data unless you are prepared to recalibrate.  




\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
Calibration data container for Aurora This data is calibrated from the Qu-\/\+Bit default Aurora firmware. It is advised not to save over this data unless you are prepared to recalibrate. 

{\ttfamily \#include $<$aurora.\+h$>$}
